---
// Honest E-E-A-T methodology block. We are research-led, not a test lab.
interface Props { heading?: string }
const { heading = 'How we choose' } = Astro.props as Props;
---
<section class="my-10 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-5 md:p-6">
  <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-soil-900 mb-3">{heading}</h2>
  <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">
    We don't run a test lab and we don't pretend to. Our recommendations are built from
    published manufacturer specifications, verified owner reviews on Amazon UK and retailer
    sites, and UK pricing data, cross-checked so the numbers on this page match the numbers
    you'll find on the box. Where a figure is the maker's claim rather than an independent
    measurement, we say so.
  </p>
  <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
    Rankings are based on cut quality, battery and runtime for the garden size in question,
    weight, build, and value at UK prices. We update picks when models are discontinued or
    superseded. We earn affiliate commission on some links, but it never decides the order of
    a list. <a href="/about/" class="text-grass-700 underline underline-offset-2">More on our method</a>.
  </p>
</section>
